# Server Backend Agent

Authoritative multiplayer server. Hub: `GameRoom` per lobby.

- Entry: `server/src/index.ts` → `LobbyManager`, `SocketGateway`, `GameLoop`, `PersistenceService`.
- Tick: 20 Hz simulation; sync: 10 Hz via `SyncBroadcaster` (delta + periodic full).
- Client intentions: `player:join`, `player:move`, `building:order`, `player:reconnect`.
- Validate all input via `InputValidator`; rate-limit per socket.
- New gameplay state flows through `WorldStateManager.markDirty()` → delta broadcast.
